        Returns:
        API response of fetch for the given input keyword

      • search

        public java.util.concurrent.CompletionStage<play.mvc.Result> search(java.lang.String inputKeyword)
        An action that renders an HTML page with 10 latest projects of given keyword and it will be rendered on the top of the previous result of projects.
